Simulation Pattern Based on MOB

Code to Generate Figures: numZero=10, sigzero = 1.

rm(list=ls())
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/freq_func.R")
source("/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/SDE/mulan_temp/common_function/simple_plot.R")

library(ggpubr)
numZero = 10
sigzero = 1
isid = 1

layerlist <- c("E","EPL","ONL","GL")
datapath = "/net/mulan/disk2/jiaqiang/kdc/experiment/simulation/v3/data/rds/"
all_figs <- list()
icount = 0
for(iblock in c(10,15,20,25)){
    icount = icount + 1
    pp <- list()
    for(ilayer in 1:4){
        load(paste0(datapath,"/sim_data_CN24_E1_",iblock,"X_",layerlist[ilayer],"_zero",numZero,"_sigzero",sigzero,"_rpt",isid,".rds"))
        pltdat  <- cbind.data.frame(location[,1:2],relative_func(sp_sim_count[1,]))
        pp[[ilayer]]     <- pattern_plot3_italic(pltdat,1,main=T,pointsize=3,titlesize=1.5,min.pand=0.9,max.pand=1.01,title=layerlist[ilayer])
        rm(pltdat,location,sp_sim_count)
    }
    all_figs[[icount]] <- ggarrange(pp[[1]], pp[[2]], pp[[3]],pp[[4]],
            ncol = 4, nrow = 1)
    rm(pp)
}
